  "<b>Part 5: Class Exercise</b>:<br><br>Answer the following questions:<br><br>1. What happens to the leaves of trees in fall?<br>2. Name three things you might wear when the weather becomes cooler in fall.<br>3. True or False: Fall is the warmest season of the year.<br>4. What colors do the leaves turn during fall?<br>5. Can you name one food that is harvested in the fall?<br>6. True or False: Animals like squirrels gather food in the fall.<br>7. What is a harvest festival?<br>8. Why do trees lose their leaves in fall?<br>9. What do you notice about the weather in fall compared to summer?<br>10. Can you think of an activity people do in the fall that involves pumpkins?"
